 Port Elizabeth - The South African National Roads Agency SOC Ltd (SANRAL) would like to notify travellers that roadworks is scheduled to take place on the R75 between Port Elizabeth and Despatch from Monday, 06 May 2019 to Thursday, 09 May 2019. The planned traffic accommodation is as follows: “Motorists are asked to plan their trips accordingly, consider alternative routes and to use caution when making use of the road,” Mbulelo Peterson, SANRAL Southern Region’s Manager said. SANRAL apologizes for any inconvenience caused. Follow more RNEWS articles, subscribe to our YouTube channel and for breaking news LIKE us on Facebook. For news on the Western Cape click here. 